ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 22nd day of October, 2008, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus and/or Extraordinary Relief and the Motion for Recognizance or Bail are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
